map_npcs.name: Researcher Dale
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Yeah, that's about what I figured would happen.
Anyway you're here for the flower's sample, right?
Go ahead and take some, the Katerina already took some for herself so the specimen's basically ruined anyway.
I should get back to my work and stop overthinking things.
You stay safe out there!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Hmmm...but if the flower's roots go that deep...
And the genetic makeup of Oochamon...
Wouldn't that mean that...
Oh! Sorry, I didn't see you there, you want a battle right?

map_npcs.name: Relaxing Crew
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ah, won't you come bask with us?
No? That's fine, take these...

map_npcs.name: Raider Syl
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Well if it's not your fault, who's is it? 
Somebody's got some explaining to do!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
What's with this place? Half the folks around here are acting strange!
You! Was it you?!

map_npcs.name: Scout Ray
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Hmmm?
Yes... I am... scouting...
Ah, the flowers... are beautiful...
Stay... Enjoy...
No?
No!?

map_npcs.name: CHANGE THIS YA DINGUS
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue:
Ah, that's better.
I think I'll go bother her after I get some rest in!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
My coworker is acting all weird!
Have you seen how she's running that shop?
I need to cool my head. How about a quick battle to pass the time?

map_npcs.name: Explorer Dave
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
*yawn*
I could just... take a nap here...
Don't worry, I'll catch up with ya pal...
Oh... and these... *yawn*

map_shops.greeting_dialog: Hello... welcome to my... store? Purchase, yes...
map_shops.greeting_dialogue: Welcome to my store. Buy whatever you need below!
